And then things will become adversarial.

23:03.632 --> 23:05.092
The deal's gone. Forget the deal.

23:05.884 --> 23:08.470
Is that what you want? Us against you?

23:09.763 --> 23:12.432
Knowin' what I know about you?
You want me against you?

23:12.557 --> 23:13.809
