this is a whole separate deal.

28:25.245 --> 28:28.206
This is a whole new trial.
More time. Put 'em together.

28:30.166 --> 28:31.209
I didn't do that one.

28:33.169 --> 28:36.339
Okay. I want you to listen to me, okay?

28:36.673 --> 28:39.634
You got the one robbery.
You put it with the other four,

28:39.968 --> 28:43.555
