they're gonna find a place for you.

29:01.281 --> 29:02.490
So, put 'em together.

29:06.453 --> 29:09.706
Okay, let me tell you what's gonna happen
if you don't cooperate, Luis.

29:10.373 --> 29:13.126
My lieutenant is gonna have me look
into all the cab robberies

29:13.126 --> 29:14.377
in the last six months.

29:14.627 --> 29:17.505
