he's gonna want me to connect them to?

29:17.881 --> 29:19.758
Who do you think? Huh?

29:20.216 --> 29:23.720
It's gonna take me
three or four days, but I'll do it.

29:24.888 --> 29:26.222
No, that don't make sense.

29:28.892 --> 29:30.977
Luis, you're probably feeling
like you're being jerked around,

29:31.227 --> 29:32.896
and I'm partially responsible for that.

29:32.896 --> 29:35.190
I should've looked
into more files before we talked.

29:35.899 --> 29:38.985
So, I'm gonna make it up to you.
I'm gonna sweeten the pot a little, okay?

29:39.402 --> 29:40.445
Right.

29:42.071 --> 29:43.990
Tell me how you feel
about the crimes you committed.

29:47.619 --> 29:48.703
Bad. I feel bad.

29:49.204 --> 29:52.540
And sittin' here, hearin' you say that,
I believe you are sincere.

29:52.665 --> 29:56.252
So, what I'm gonna do is, when you make
the second confession on tape,

29:56.252 --> 29:58.671
at the end of the tape,
I'm gonna allow you

29:59.130 --> 30:01.466
to make a statement
of remorse to the judge.

30:02.550 --> 30:04.719
That's important, Luis.
They want remorse.

30:05.261 --> 30:07.472
You got money problems.
You're desperate for money.

30:07.472 --> 30:10.433
You can't make your rent.
Right? That make sense?

30:12.644 --> 30:13.686
Think about it.

30:19.400 --> 30:22.487
So, after you bound
the driver's wrists with duct tape,

30:22.487 --> 30:24.781
and made him leave the cab,
then what did you do?

30:26.991 --> 30:28.701
I drove the cab to 24th Street

30:28.701 --> 30:30.662
'cause I knew
there was a subway stop near there.

30:33.206 --> 30:35.667
I counted the money.

30:36.251 --> 30:37.335
There was, um...

30:38.628 --> 30:42.382
Fifty-five... no, 58 dollars.

30:44.717 --> 30:47.762
- And then I just left the cab.
- You took the subway home?

30:48.805 --> 30:49.806
Yeah.

30:52.725 --> 30:54.227
- Now?
- Yeah, go ahead.

30:57.730 --> 31:00.650
I just wanna say I'm very sorry
for doin' these robberies.

31:01.901 --> 31:03.152
I know that they were wrong.

31:04.863 --> 31:07.532
I didn't use the money for drugs
or any illegal things.

31:09.117 --> 31:11.160
Uh, these are
the only crimes I've ever done.

31:15.331 --> 31:16.332
You're the man.

31:16.749 --> 31:19.961
Nice job.

31:20.336 --> 31:21.880
Hurry it up down there.

31:23.756 --> 31:25.049
- Detective Sipowicz.
- Yeah?

31:25.633 --> 31:28.887
I don't care if you embarrass yourself
but don't embarrass me.

31:29.095 --> 31:31.848
Excuse me, Counselor. I, uh,
I'm not sure I'm taking your drift.

31:32.140 --> 31:35.435
I've just come from an interview
with your arrestee, Frank Cantor,

31:35.852 --> 31:39.355
